The paper focuses on learning hybrid systems for robotics, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The approach involves learning from demonstrations, which suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of visual perception networks also suggests a focus on computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the paper discusses the use of grammar parsing strategies, which suggests a focus on systems and control (cs.SY).
